{"tid":1087223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】天水圍黃大仙網上呃人狗男女","createTime":"2019-04-01T08:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T04:41:55.000Z","uid":229304,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8d149aeb3868bf0765931657063fcc699a545033","tid":1087223,"uid":229304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"大家請小心, 真人真事. 已經有人中招。<br />\n<br />\n男住天水圍，叫周俊傑<br />\n facebook : Valentine Chau, ig: leonpet1992<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女住黃大仙竹園，只知姓崔<br />\n facebook : Cui Cui, ig : Canmanb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/959685480735461?view=permalink&amp;id=1794554357248565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F959685480735461%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D1794554357248565&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=700c1245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/959685480735461?view=permalink&amp;id=1794554357248565</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://carousell.com/scooterscam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcarousell.com%2Fscooterscam&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f76e4ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://carousell.com/scooterscam</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖中兩個 Carosusell 戶口, 出沒喺屯門及元朗及深圳福田一帶. 佢話自己係專業維修電動滑板車,iphone, macbook, 佢出嚟時會帶帽口罩, 話自己冇手提電話. 話全部柯打都係由佢女朋友安排. 佢話大約兩三日會整好, 不過然後會將你件物件私有化. 跟住唔再聽你電話同覆你message.有位師兄 畀佢呃咗買粒壞嘅i7cpu 又唔見千幾。 搵都搵唔到佢。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n過咗兩三個月你唔再搵唔到佢, 佢會將你件嘢兩賣返出去. 不過呢條笨賊又蠢又冇人性, 7到竟然仲夠膽喺 Carousell 賣返賊贓出去, 仲要搵佢女朋友去交收. 自己喺附近匿埋一二角驚畀人認出.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n仲有如果有人話落訂可以買到平嘅電動滑板車, 本人覺得應該係同一個賣家, 佢專係抄人啲相然後開post. 大家請小心最好當面落訂. 如果見到係佢大家知點做<br />\n<br />\n佢仲有iPhone, apple 同其他電子產品維，一係就賣有問題嘅機，同你發現時，佢就會Block 咗你。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人渣 真名叫周X傑 花名叫萬子網名就叫 Leon. 住天X圍 x恒邨 x麗樓 11樓。 周圍欺騙無知少女 ，食軟飯為人生目標， 專搵朋友笨七， 借錢唔還 ， 周身街數 。 話自己係做市場策劃話自己搵兩三萬蚊一個月 佢冇咩朋友冇畀佢呃過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSk57hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSk57hf.jpg&h=f15fb522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Di11FCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDi11FCg.jpg&h=4c3013b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHbdwJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHbdwJX.jpg&h=ec16bbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dkFbJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dkFbJY.jpg&h=e61544f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1TCYoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1TCYoY.jpg&h=0454c7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVvU0Cj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVvU0Cj.jpg&h=e15a66d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PtwMRJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPtwMRJZ.jpg&h=774d6526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVvhYo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVvhYo0.jpg&h=a000fb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdwtkCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdwtkCm.jpg&h=5b41d673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDX0WaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDX0WaH.jpg&h=454ef9b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49cd0aea12242b275a520f4b62b7cc3bc8b9c82c","tid":1087223,"uid":649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，條仔咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲推條女去交收"},{"pid":"fbe220bc8e6fc9d90dbc706303a134f11355ff31","tid":1087223,"uid":229304,"like":3,"dislike"